NK132(no)006:1: // smon lam rdo rje'i tshig gi rgya mdud kyi 'grel ba bzhugs so //
NK132(no)006:2: dngos po'i spros mtshan kun las rab zhi yang //
NK132(no)006:3: 'gag med ye shes sgyu ma'i rol gar gyis //
NK132(no)006:4: mtha' yas 'gro la phan bde'i mchog stsol ba //
NK132(no)006:5: khyab bdag 'jam dpal dpa' bos 'gro 'di skyongs //
NK132(no)006:6: rnam dkar dge ba'i dngos po lcags kyi khams //
NK132(no)006:7: thabs mkhas grub pa'i bcud kyis zin pa na //
NK132(no)006:8: rnam grol sku bzhi'i dbyig tu grub pa'i phyir //
NK132(no)006:9: smon pa'i mchog 'dir brtson pa don rab ldan //
NK132(no)006:10: de la 'dir dge ba'i rtsa ba gang zhig bla na med pa'i byang chub tu smin cing /
NK132(no)006:11: mi mthun pa'i phyogs kyis mi zad cing gong nas
NK132(no)006:12: gong du spel ba'i thabs khyad par can ni yongs
NK132(no)006:13: su bsngo zhing smon lam gyis rgyas 'debs pa yin
NK132(no)006:14: zhing / smon lam de la rnam grangs bsam gyis
NK132(no)006:15: mi khyab pa yod na yang skabs 'dir nang rgyud
NK132(no)006:16: sde gsum gyi brjod bya zab cing rgya che ba
NK132(no)006:17: dang rjes su 'brel ba'i smon lam gyi rgyal po'i
NK132(no)006:18: rnam gzhag cung zad cig 'chad pa la /
NK132(no)006:19: bsngo ba'i dpang por gsol ba /
NK132(no)006:20: bsngo rgyu'i dge rtsa bstan pa /
NK132(no)006:21: bsngo ba dngos dang gsum las /
NK132(no)006:23: bla ma yi dam lha tshogs dgongs su gsol //
NK132(no)006:25: brgyud gsum gyi bla ma yi dam zhi khro rab 'byams dang /
NK132(no)006:26: gzhan yang dpa' bo mkha' 'gro rdo rje chos skyong
NK132(no)006:27: ba'i srung mar bcas pa'i rtsa gsum lhag pa'i lha
NK132(no)006:28: tshogs til gyi gong bu kha phyes pa ltar mngon
NK132(no)006:29: sum bzhin du bzhugs pa thams cad ye shes sgrib
NK132(no)006:30: pa med pa'i gzigs pas bdag la dgongs su gsol
NK132(no)006:32: deng 'dir brtson pas bsgrubs pa'i dge ba dang /
NK132(no)006:33: dus gsum bsags dang yod pa'i dge ba rnams //
NK132(no)006:34: bsdoms te zhes deng 'dir gus rtag gi brtson pas
NK132(no)006:35: lam rim pa gnyis rnal 'byor tshul bzhin du bsgrubs
NK132(no)006:37: des mtshon pa'i rang gis dus gsum du bsags pa'i dge ba thams cad dang /
NK132(no)006:38: rang gis bsags pa min yang sems can gzhan rgyud
NK132(no)006:39: du grub pa'am yod pa'i dge ba rnams kyang blos
NK132(no)006:40: phyogs gcig tu bsdoms te gnas pa ni gang bsngo
NK132(no)006:41: rgyu'i dge ba'o // de la kha cig 'di snyam du /
NK132(no)006:42: rang gis da lta'i dge ba da lta ba yin la /
NK132(no)006:43: de'i rjes su dus gsum ston pas da lta ba gang la ngos 'dzin snyam na /
NK132(no)006:44: dang po da lta sgrub bzhin pa'i dge ba de gtso bor smros la /
NK132(no)006:45: de dag tu ma 'dus pa gzhan dus gsum ci rigs kyi khungs su 'du bas /
NK132(no)006:46: spyir rgya che ba nas smos pa'i spyi dang bye
NK132(no)006:47: brag gi khyad par yod pas zlos par mi 'gyur
NK132(no)006:48: ro // yang kha cig 'di snyam du 'das da
NK132(no)006:49: ltar gyi dge ba mi mthun phyogs kyis ma bcos
NK132(no)006:50: pa bsngo ru btub na yang /
NK132(no)006:51: ma 'ongs pa'i dge ba la sogs pa mi 'thad de /
NK132(no)006:52: de dag da lta med pa'i phyir /
NK132(no)006:53: ri bong gi rwa bzhin snyam na /
NK132(no)006:54: byang chub sems dpa'i thabs la mkhas pa'i 'dun pas
NK132(no)006:55: dmigs pa thams cad byang chub chen po'i lam du
NK132(no)006:56: gtong ba la 'gal ba med de /
NK132(no)006:57: bdag gi ma 'ongs pa'i sgo gsum gyi 'jug pa
NK132(no)006:58: thams cad sems can thams cad rnam par grol ba'i
NK132(no)006:59: don du shog cig snyam na /
NK132(no)006:60: ma 'ongs pa'i rang gi sgo gsum gyi las dang /
NK132(no)006:61: des phan 'dogs pa'i yul sems can da lta na yod pa min yang /
NK132(no)006:62: blo'i stobs kyis de ltar bsam pas ma 'ongs pa'i
NK132(no)006:63: sems can la phan 'dogs par nus pa bzhin te
NK132(no)006:64: byang chub sems dpa'i blo gros kyi khyad chos so
NK132(no)006:65: // gsum pa la mthar thug gi 'bras bu'i ched du bsngo ba /
NK132(no)006:66: gnas skabs kyi lam gyi ched du bsngo ba //
NK132(no)006:67: bstan pa dang 'gro ba'i don du bsngo ba dang gsum las /
NK132(no)006:69: bla med byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK132(no)006:70: zhes de lta bu'i dge rtsa de dag gi phyir
NK132(no)006:71: bsngosa na gnas skabs lha mi'i go 'phang tsam don
NK132(no)006:72: du gnyer te mngon mtho'i phyir bsngo ba min cing
NK132(no)006:73: / rang don zhi ba phyogs gcig pa'i ched du'ang ma yin la /
NK132(no)006:74: thob bya mthar thug gi 'bras bu bla na med
NK132(no)006:75: pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub chen por
NK132(no)006:76: bsngo ba ste / rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes thob pa kho na'i phyir bsngo ba'o //
NK132(no)006:78: lam gyi rten du bsngo ba /
NK132(no)006:82: lam gyi mthun rkyen tshang bar bsngo ba'o //
NK132(no)006:84: deng nas byang chub snying por mchis kyi bar //
NK132(no)006:85: rigs bzang blo gsal nga rgyal med pa dang //
NK132(no)006:86: snying rje che zhing bla ma la gus ldan //
NK132(no)006:87: dpal ldan rdo rje'i theg la nges gnas shog /
NK132(no)006:88: deng gi dus 'di nas bzung ste ji srid byang
NK132(no)006:89: chub snying por mchis te mngon par sangs rgyas kyi
NK132(no)006:90: bar du theg pa mchog gi rigs yongs su sad
NK132(no)006:91: pas na rigs bzang po gser lta bu nyid du
NK132(no)006:92: 'gyur ba dang / theg pa mchog gi lam gsang
NK132(no)006:93: rtogs nus pa'i blo gros shin tu gsal ba dang
NK132(no)006:94: 'gyur ba dang / / rang rgyud la yon tan
NK132(no)006:95: skye ba'i gegs su gyur pa'i nga rgyal med pa
NK132(no)006:96: 'gyur ba dang / / dang / sems can yongs
NK132(no)006:97: su mi 'dor ba'i snying rje chen po'i rgyud yongs
NK132(no)006:98: 'gyur ba dang / / dang / su gang zhing
NK132(no)006:99: / lam gyi rtsa ba mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i
NK132(no)006:100: bla ma mchog la mi 'gyur ba'i gus pa dang
NK132(no)006:101: ldan pa'i sgo nas don gnyis sam dngos grub rnam
NK132(no)006:102: pa gnyis bde blag tu 'grub pa'i dpal dang ldan
NK132(no)006:103: par gnyis med kyi ye shes rdo rje lta bu
NK132(no)006:104: gzhig cing gzhom du med pa la 'degs shing sbyor
NK132(no)006:105: ba'i lam ni theg pa ste /
NK132(no)006:106: des rdo rje'i theg pa zhes yongs su grags pa la /
NK132(no)006:107: dbang gis smin pa sogs 'og nas 'chad 'gyur ltar
NK132(no)006:108: gyi yon tan dang ldan pas sngags la zhugs tsam
NK132(no)006:109: gyi gzugs brnyan lta bu ma yin par mtshan nyid
NK132(no)006:110: dang ldan pa'i tshul bzhin du gnas pa la nges
NK132(no)006:111: par gnas par shog cig ces gsungs te /
NK132(no)006:112: mdor na theg pa chen po sngar gdul bya thun
NK132(no)006:113: mong ma yin pa'i rigs su nges pa gzhir bzhag
NK132(no)006:114: nas lam gyi dngos gzhi chos thams cad lhag pa'i
NK132(no)006:115: bden pa dbyer med du gtan la 'bebs nus pa'i
NK132(no)006:116: shes rab dang / sems can thams cad kyi don
NK132(no)006:117: du myur ba myur bar sangs rgyas thob 'dod kyi
NK132(no)006:118: snying rje gnyis dang ldan zhing lam rgyud la skye
NK132(no)006:119: ba'i gegs nga rgyal spangs shing mthun rkyen mos pa
NK132(no)006:120: phun sum tshogs pa ste med du mi rung ba'i
NK132(no)006:121: yon tan gyi khyad par de dag dang ldan pa'i
NK132(no)006:122: sgo nas dpal ldan rdo rje'i theg pa la nges
NK132(no)006:123: par gnas pa nyid du shog cig ces so //
NK132(no)006:125: lam spyi'i ched du bsngo ba dang /
NK132(no)006:126: bye brag so so'i ched du bsngo ba'o //
NK132(no)006:128: dbang gis smin cing dam tshig sdom par ldan //
NK132(no)006:129: rim gnyis lam la bsnyen sgrub mthar phyin nas //
NK132(no)006:130: dka' ba med par rig 'dzin go 'phang bgrod //
NK132(no)006:131: dngos grub rnam gnyis bde blag 'grub gyur cig /
NK132(no)006:133: sems can thams cad kyi rgyud la gnyug ma'i rtsa
NK132(no)006:134: rlung thig le sems dang bcas pa sku gsung thugs
NK132(no)006:135: ye shes rdo rje'i bsgrub gzhir gnas pa nyid dbang
NK132(no)006:136: bzhi'i sgo nas sad par byas shing sku bzhir smin
NK132(no)006:137: rung gi nus pa khyad par can rgyud la 'jog
NK132(no)006:138: pa ste / de yang gang zag gi dbang po'i
NK132(no)006:139: bye brag la ltos pa'i go myong rtogs pa gsum
NK132(no)006:140: gyi tshul du dbang don gyi ye shes la nges
NK132(no)006:141: pa ci rigs 'drangs pa ni lam bsgom rung dang
NK132(no)006:142: 'bras bu thob rung gi rgyur 'gyur bas na dbang
NK132(no)006:143: gis smin pa zhes gsungs pa yin la /
NK132(no)006:144: de ni gsang sngags kyi lam thams cad kyi 'jug sgo yin cing /
NK132(no)006:145: de ltar dbang thob pa tsam gyis mi chog ste /
NK132(no)006:146: dbang gi srog dam tshig dang sdom pas tshul bzhin
NK132(no)006:147: du ma bzung na dngos grub rnam pa gnyis mi
NK132(no)006:148: thob pas skyon spang ba'i cha nas sdom pa dang
NK132(no)006:149: / yon tan bsgrub pa'i cha nas dam tshig ste /
NK132(no)006:150: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig 'da' bar
NK132(no)006:151: bya ba ma yin pa'i gnas rnams kyis nyes lhung
NK132(no)006:152: gi dri ma mtha' dag sdom par byed pa dang
NK132(no)006:153: ldan pa / de ltar dbang gis smin cing dam
NK132(no)006:154: tshig dang sdom par ldan pa'i gang zag des bskyed
NK132(no)006:155: rdzogs rim pa gnyis kyi lam la bsnyen pa dang
NK132(no)006:156: sgrub pa mthar phyin nas dka' ba med par rig
NK132(no)006:157: 'dzin rnam pa bzhi'i go 'phang myur du bgrod de
NK132(no)006:158: ldan pa / / kha sbyor yan lag bdun dang ldan pa mchog gi dngos grub dang /
NK132(no)006:159: grub pa dang dbang phyug brgyad la sogs pa thun mong gi dngos grub ste /
NK132(no)006:160: dngos grub rnam pa gnyis po dka' tshegs dang yun
NK132(no)006:161: ring du 'bad mi dgos par bde blag tu 'grub
NK132(no)006:163: de la bsnyen sgrub bzhi dang sbyar tshul du ma yod kyang /
NK132(no)006:164: bskyed rim dang sbyar na stong chen dang snying rje sgyu ma bsnyen pa /
NK132(no)006:165: phyag rgya phra rag nye bsnyen /
NK132(no)006:166: spros bcas nas bsam yas lhun grub kyi dkyil 'khor bsgom pa'i bar sgrub pa /
NK132(no)006:167: tshom bu tshogs sgrub kyi dngos grub blangs pa bsgrub pa chen po'o //
NK132(no)006:169: kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems rten dang brten par bcas pa'i gnad shes pa bsnyen pa /
NK132(no)006:170: rang byung lus gnas kyi dkyil 'khor gsal zhing de la gnad du bsnun pa nye bsnyen /
NK132(no)006:171: phyag rgya mo byin gyis brlab pa sgrub pa /
NK132(no)006:172: yab yum snyoms par zhugs pa'i bde chen dpe don gyi ye shes ni sgrub pa chen po'o //
NK132(no)006:173: gnyis ka dang sbyar na dbang bzhi'i lam bskyed rdzogs
NK132(no)006:174: sogs dang bsnyen sgrub bzhi po rim par sbyar ro
NK132(no)006:176: rgyud sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i nyams len la smon pa /
NK132(no)006:177: lung na rag dong sprugs kyi nyams len la smon pa /
NK132(no)006:178: man ngag rdzogs pa chen po'i nyams len la smon pa dang gsum las /
NK132(no)006:180: snang ba sku yi dkyil 'khor la smon pa /
NK132(no)006:181: sgra grags gsung gi dkyil 'khor la smon pa /
NK132(no)006:182: dran rtog thugs kyi dkyil 'khor la smon pa /
NK132(no)006:183: thams cad bde chen gyi rol pa la smon pa'o //
NK132(no)006:185: cir snang sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i 'khor lo rdzogs //
NK132(no)006:187: phyi nang snod bcud kyi dngos po cir snang ba
NK132(no)006:188: thams cad tha mal rang mtshan gyi zhen pa log
NK132(no)006:189: ste / snang stong sku rdo rje sku 'phrul d+r+wa
NK132(no)006:190: ba zhes sgyu ma ltar 'phrul zhing mang la 'brel
NK132(no)006:191: ste / ba'i d+r+wa ba'am / yang na cir snang
NK132(no)006:192: gi dngos po sgyu ma lta bu rnams rang bzhin
NK132(no)006:193: rnam par dag pa'i lha'i ngo bor 'phrul pa'am shar
NK132(no)006:194: ste / ba'i d+r+wa ba'am / zhing / de ltar
NK132(no)006:195: lha dang rtog tshogs dbyer med du 'brel ba'am mnyam
NK132(no)006:196: pa'i don du zhes bshad de /
NK132(no)006:197: gang ltar yang mdor na cir snang gi dngos po
NK132(no)006:198: thams cad sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba lha yi 'khor lo'am
NK132(no)006:199: tshogs sam rang bzhin du 'byams klas pa ste snang
NK132(no)006:200: ba thams cad sku rdo rje'i ngo bor rdzogs pa'o
NK132(no)006:202: grags pa thams cad brjod bral sngags kyi sgra /
NK132(no)006:203: zhes sgra grags pa thams cad grags tsam nyid nas
NK132(no)006:204: rang gi ngo bos stong pa'i grags stong zung 'jug
NK132(no)006:206: brjod pa dang bral ba'i gsang sngags kyi sgra gdangs shar ba'o //
NK132(no)006:208: sems kyi 'gyu ba rang rig 'dus ma byas //
NK132(no)006:209: zhes sems kyi rnam par rtog pa'i 'gyu ba sna
NK132(no)006:210: tshogs pa gsal ba stong pa zung du 'jug pa'i
NK132(no)006:211: rang rig 'dus ma byas pa'i dbyings 'od gsal thugs
NK132(no)006:212: kyi rdo rje nyid du shar ba'o //
NK132(no)006:214: bde chen 'du 'bral med pa mngon gyur shog /
NK132(no)006:215: ces de ltar snang grags rtog pa'i chos thams cad
NK132(no)006:216: bde ba chen po rig stong zung 'jug ye shes
NK132(no)006:217: rdo rje nyag gcig gi rol par shar ba ste
NK132(no)006:218: / de yang tha mal gyi rnam par rtog pa thams cad sdug bsngal yin la /
NK132(no)006:219: de dang bral ba gang yin pa bde ba ste /
NK132(no)006:220: de yang gzhom gzhig dang bral zhing bla na med pas na chen po'o //
NK132(no)006:221: de lta bu'i bde ba chen po'i ye shes de
NK132(no)006:222: 'khor 'das brtan g.yon thams cad la khyab pas srid
NK132(no)006:223: zhi kun khyab kyi ye shes zhes bya ste /
NK132(no)006:224: dngos po'i chos gang yang ma spangs dngos po'i chos
NK132(no)006:225: gang la'ang mi gnas pa'i rang bzhin rang byung ye
NK132(no)006:226: shes nyag gcig gi klong du 'khor 'das thams cad
NK132(no)006:227: rdzogs pa ste / de yang chos rnams dang gsar du 'du ba dang /
NK132(no)006:228: slar yang 'bral ba lta bu ma yin par gdod
NK132(no)006:229: nas 'dul 'bral med pa'i de kho na nyid ye
NK132(no)006:230: shes rdo rjer mngon du 'gyur bar shog cig ces
NK132(no)006:231: pa'o // de lta bu'i sku gsung thugs ye shes
NK132(no)006:232: rdo rje'i rang bzhin du shar ba'i gnad 'di la
NK132(no)006:233: yang bskyed rdzogs so so dang sbyar na sku gsung
NK132(no)006:234: thugs de kho na nyid kyi rnal 'byor la brtson
NK132(no)006:235: pa'o // pa dang / sgyu lus dang /
NK132(no)006:236: rlung sngags mi shigs pa'i bzlas pa dang /
NK132(no)006:238: zung 'jug gi rnal 'byor bsgoms pa'i stobs kyis goms
NK132(no)006:239: pa klong du gyur pa'i 'bras bu yin pa rig
NK132(no)006:240: par bya'o // yang na dbang bzhi dang 'brel ba'i
NK132(no)006:241: lam bzhi bsgom pa las su rung ba'i 'bras bu
NK132(no)006:242: snang srid dag pa rab 'byams su shar ba'i gnad
NK132(no)006:243: par bya'o // yin par blta'o // gnyis pa la'ang /
NK132(no)006:244: sgrib pa ye dag gi bshags pa /
NK132(no)006:245: yon tan ye ldan gyi skong ba /
NK132(no)006:247: 'bras bu ngan song dong sprugs so //
NK132(no)006:249: nyams chags rtog sgrib ma spangs gnas su dag /
NK132(no)006:250: ces nyon mongs pa'i dbang gis rang rgyud kyi dam
NK132(no)006:251: tshig nyams shing nyams pa'i skyon de dag gnyen pos
NK132(no)006:252: ma bcom par lcags la btsa' ltar chags shing zhen
NK132(no)006:254: snod bcud rgyud rnams ngo bo'i gnas tshul dag pa
NK132(no)006:255: lha'i rang bzhin yin kyang phung sogs tha mal du
NK132(no)006:257: de lta bu'i bshags bya nyams chags dang rtog sgrib
NK132(no)006:258: de dag bshags tshul ci lta bus bshags na bcos
NK132(no)006:259: shing bsgyur ba / spangs shing zad pa lta bu
NK132(no)006:260: ma yin par rang rang gi ngo bo la gdod
NK132(no)006:261: nas bden par grub pa med pas gnyen po gzhan
NK132(no)006:262: gyis bcom zhing ma spangs par rang babs su bzhag
NK132(no)006:263: pas rang rang gi gnas ye shes su dag pa
NK132(no)006:264: shing bsgyur ba / ste / thag pa la sbrul 'dzin gyi blo zhig pa lta bu'o //
NK132(no)006:266: phyi nang gsang ba dbyer med rtogs pas bskang //
NK132(no)006:267: zhes phyi yo byad rdzas kyis bskang ba sman gtor rak+ta mar me dngos su bshams pa dang /
NK132(no)006:268: nang phung po rten gyis bskang ba ni phyi'i yo
NK132(no)006:269: byad rnams mtshon byed du byas te nang gi khu
NK132(no)006:270: rdul rlung gsum 'od gsal ba'i sems dang bcas pa
NK132(no)006:271: sman sogs su shes pa dang /
NK132(no)006:272: gsang ba byang chub kyi sems gsal ba stong pa
NK132(no)006:273: zung du 'jug pa rig pa'i ye shes mtha' dang
NK132(no)006:274: bral ba / skyon ka dag yon tan ye ldan
NK132(no)006:275: chos kyi dbyings la mnyam par bzhag pa gsum gyi
NK132(no)006:277: de la skong ba zhes bya ba yon tan gyi
NK132(no)006:278: rnam pa nyams shing kha 'phri ba de rang sor
NK132(no)006:279: chud par bya ba yin no //
NK132(no)006:280: de la tshul ji lta bus bskang na /
NK132(no)006:281: sngar med gsar bzhag lta bu ma yin par yon
NK132(no)006:282: tan ye ldan dbyer med kyi don rtogs pas bskang
NK132(no)006:283: ba ste / phyi snod dang nang lus kyi dngos
NK132(no)006:284: po thams cad gsang ba byang chub kyi sems su
NK132(no)006:286: snang srid kyi dngos po thams cad dag pa ye
NK132(no)006:287: shes kyi ngo bor dbyer med du rtogs pas bskang
NK132(no)006:288: ba ste / yon tan thams cad 'bad med ye ldan du bskang ba'o //
NK132(no)006:290: nang phung po lnga gsang ba rnam shes tshogs brgyad
NK132(no)006:291: rnams yum lnga rigs lnga ye shes lnga yi ngo
NK132(no)006:292: bor dag pa'am gdod nas dbyer med pa'i don rtogs
NK132(no)006:293: pas rtog tshogs lha'i rang bzhin du bskang ba'o //
NK132(no)006:294: de ltar bshags skong gnyis po 'di byang chub kyi
NK132(no)006:295: sems lhag pa'i bden pa dbyer med du rtogs pa'i
NK132(no)006:296: gshis la spang bya'i dri ma ma spangs par dag
NK132(no)006:297: pa dang / chos kyi dbyings su zag pa med
NK132(no)006:298: pa'i yon tan rnams 'bral med du gnas pas yon
NK132(no)006:299: tan ye ldan gyi tshul du bskang ba ste theg
NK132(no)006:300: pa chen po'i khyad chos bsal bzhag med pa'i gnad
NK132(no)006:301: pa dang / de / 'di la bsal bya ci yang med //
NK132(no)006:302: bzhag par bya ba gang yang med //
NK132(no)006:305: gang shar rang grol kun bzang klong yangs su //
NK132(no)006:307: mtshon byed rtags kyi kun tu bzang po la brten
NK132(no)006:308: nas mtshon bya don gyi kun tu bzang po ngo
NK132(no)006:309: 'phrod pa na rnam rtog gang shar ba thams cad
NK132(no)006:310: chu dang rlabs bzhin rang sar rang grol bas kun
NK132(no)006:311: nas dor bya ma dag rang mtshan pa'i chos mi
NK132(no)006:312: rnyed par kun tu bzang po'i dgongs pa'i klong yangs
NK132(no)006:313: su snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad mnyam
NK132(no)006:314: par brdal ba ni nyams kun tu bzang po'o //
NK132(no)006:316: ngan song dong sprugs srid zhi mnyam gyur cig /
NK132(no)006:317: ces de ltar rgyu nyon mongs kyi rtog tshogs ma
NK132(no)006:318: spangs rang sar grol bas 'bras bu ngan song du
NK132(no)006:319: 'gro ba'i sa bon drungs nas phyungs te /
NK132(no)006:320: 'khor 'das spang blang gi mtshan rtog yongs su zad pas ngan song dong nas sprugs pa yin la /
NK132(no)006:321: srid pa dang zhi ba'am 'khor 'das kyi chos thams
NK132(no)006:322: cad rang byung byang chub kyi sems su ro mnyam
NK132(no)006:323: par brdal te mthar thug gi 'bras bu mngon du
NK132(no)006:324: byed par gyur cig ces pa'o //
NK132(no)006:325: gsum pa man ngag rdzogs chen la'ang /
NK132(no)006:326: thig le rang gnas gyi lta ba /
NK132(no)006:327: bsrung du med pa'i dam tshig /'du 'bral med pa'i bsgom pa /
NK132(no)006:328: spang thob bral ba'i 'bras bu dang bzhi las /
NK132(no)006:330: thig le chen po sku dang zhing khams rdzogs //
NK132(no)006:332: thig le zhes pa grwa zur med par kun nas
NK132(no)006:333: zlum pa'i don te ye stong chen por gdangs rtsal
NK132(no)006:334: lhun gyis grub pa'i ye shes sku dang zhing khams
NK132(no)006:335: rgya mtsho ma lus par rdzogs pa'i gnas lugs kyi
NK132(no)006:336: don mthong ba'o // gnyis pa ni /
NK132(no)006:337: dam tshig chen por spang blang mtshan ma dag /
NK132(no)006:338: ces snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rang
NK132(no)006:339: byung ye shes thig le nyag gcig gi ngang du
NK132(no)006:340: la bzlas pas med pa phyal pa lhun grub gcig
NK132(no)006:342: thams cad chos nyid kyi rol par shes pas de
NK132(no)006:343: las gzhan pa'i dam tshig bsrung rgyu med pa ye
NK132(no)006:344: bsrung gi dam tshig chen por spang blang gi mtshan
NK132(no)006:345: ma thams cad rang babs su dag ste /
NK132(no)006:346: bsrung med bsrung ba kun gyi rgyal po snod bcud
NK132(no)006:347: ye shes kyi 'khor lor rtogs pa'i gnad la mi
NK132(no)006:348: 'da' ba ste / 'di ni dam tshig kyang yin la spyod pa'ang don gyis 'dir 'adu'o //
NK132(no)006:350: khyab brdal chen po re dogs mdud pa grol //
NK132(no)006:351: zhes sems nyid spros bral rang byung gi ye shes
NK132(no)006:352: gcig gi klong du 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad
NK132(no)006:353: dbyer med pas na shes bya'i chos thams cad la
NK132(no)006:354: khyab par brdal ba'i 'da' bar dka' ba'i thugs kyi
NK132(no)006:355: ye shes chen por bzang ngan gyi zhen rtog zad
NK132(no)006:356: de / ris med pa'i ye shes kyi rol pa
NK132(no)006:357: 'ba' zhig las ma dag rang mtshan pa 'khor bar
NK132(no)006:358: 'ching ba'i chos shig gser gling du rdo phal pa
NK132(no)006:359: bzhin btsal kyang mi rnyed par thag chod pas bzang
NK132(no)006:361: ngan 'dod kyi dogs pas kun nas dkris pa'i 'ching
NK132(no)006:362: ba dam po'i mdud pa grol te so ma dal
NK132(no)006:363: ba rnal ma bag yangs su skyong ba'o //
NK132(no)006:365: rdzogs pa chen por chos sku mngon gyur shog /
NK132(no)006:366: ces 'khor 'das thams cad kyi gnas lugs de kho
NK132(no)006:367: na nyid chos sku thig le nyag gcig gi klong
NK132(no)006:368: na sku dang ye shes thams cad dbyer med ro
NK132(no)006:369: gcig pa'i tshul du rdzogs pas rang bzhin rdzogs pa
NK132(no)006:370: chen por rtogs goms mthar phyin pas zag med kyi
NK132(no)006:371: yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i rten du gyur
NK132(no)006:372: pa rang byung chos kyi sku rang gi ngo bo'i
NK132(no)006:373: bzhugs tshul ji lta ba bzhin mngon du gyur par
NK132(no)006:376: brgyud pa gsum gyi byin rlabs snying la zhugs /
NK132(no)006:377: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i lam bzang sems la rdzogs //
NK132(no)006:378: phrin las rnam bzhi lhun gyis grub pa yis //
NK132(no)006:379: mu mtha' med pa'i 'gro ba sgrol bar shog /
NK132(no)006:381: dgongs brda snyan brgyud de brgyud pa gsum gyi rim
NK132(no)006:382: pa las 'ong ba'i dbang bskur rgyud bshad bskyed rdzogs
NK132(no)006:383: dang bcas pa'i bka' babs kyi chu bo bzhi'i byin
NK132(no)006:384: rlabs snying la ro gcig tu zhugs shing rtog tshogs
NK132(no)006:385: lha'i ngo bor dag pa'i sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba chen
NK132(no)006:386: po'i lam gyi gsang ba'i gnad zab mo sems la
NK132(no)006:387: rdzogs pa ste ma lus pa mngon du rtogs nas
NK132(no)006:388: / thun mong dang mchog gi zhi rgyas dbang drag
NK132(no)006:389: gi phrin las rnam pa bzhi 'bad rtsol med par
NK132(no)006:391: de lta bu'i phrin las de yis nam mkha' gar
NK132(no)006:392: khyab pa'i mu dang mtha' med pa'i 'gro ba ji
NK132(no)006:393: snyed pa rnams gang la gang 'dul gyi sgo nas
NK132(no)006:394: byang chub gsum gyi lam la sgrol bar shog cig
NK132(no)006:395: ces pa'o // bzhi pa lam gyi mthun rkyen tshang ba la smon pa ni /
NK132(no)006:396: zhi khro sprul pa'i 'khor los lung ston cing //
NK132(no)006:397: mkha' 'gro rnams kyis bu bzhin skyong ba dang //
NK132(no)006:398: chos skyong srung mas bar chad kun bsal nas //
NK132(no)006:399: yid la smon pa mtha' dag 'grub gyur cig /
NK132(no)006:400: ces pa yi dam zhi ba dang khro bo rnams
NK132(no)006:401: kyi sprul pa'i 'khor los sa lam dang nyams rtogs
NK132(no)006:402: kyi gegs sel bogs 'don rang gzhan gyi don 'grub
NK132(no)006:403: pa'i tshul rnams lung du bstan pa ste /
NK132(no)006:404: de yang 'khor lo zhes yang nas yang du rgyun mi chad pa'i don du bzung ngo //
NK132(no)006:405: gnas gsum gyi dpa' bo mkha' 'gro rnams kyis bu bzhin du skyong bar mdzad pa dang /
NK132(no)006:406: ye shes dang las dang 'jig rten gyi dregs pa
NK132(no)006:407: dkar phyogs la dga' ba'i chos skyong srung mas byang
NK132(no)006:408: chub sgrub pa'i bar chad kyi 'tshe ba kun bsal
NK132(no)006:409: nas byang chub sgrub pa'i mthun rkyen yid la re
NK132(no)006:410: ba'am smon pa mtha' dag ste ma lus pa 'grub
NK132(no)006:412: gsum pa bstan 'gro'i don du bsngo ba ni /
NK132(no)006:413: rgyal ba'i bstan pa dar zhing rgyas pa dang //
NK132(no)006:414: bstan 'dzin rnams kyi bzhed pa'i don kun 'grub //
NK132(no)006:415: ma lus skye rgu'i 'gal rkyen kun zhi zhing //
NK132(no)006:416: phun tshogs mtha' dag yid bzhin 'byor gyur cig /
NK132(no)006:417: ces 'jig rten gyi phan bde mtha' dag gi rtsa
NK132(no)006:418: ba kun mkhyen rgyal ba'i lung rtogs kyi bstan pa
NK132(no)006:419: rin po che bshad dang sgrub pa'i sgo nas phyogs
NK132(no)006:420: thams cad du dar zhing gong du 'phel ba'i tshul
NK132(no)006:421: gyis rgyas la yun ring du gnas pa dang /
NK132(no)006:422: bstan pa de 'dzin pa'i skyes bu dam pa rnams
NK132(no)006:423: kyis bstan 'gro'i dpal yon spel ba'i bzhed pa'i don
NK132(no)006:424: 'khor lo gsum gyi mdzad bzang thams cad kun nas
NK132(no)006:425: gegs med yid bzhin du 'grub pa dang /
NK132(no)006:426: ma lus shing lus pa med pa'i skye rgu'i 'gal
NK132(no)006:427: rkyen du gyur pa gnas skabs mthar thug gi 'jig
NK132(no)006:428: rten gyi rgud pa'i tshogs kun mtha' dag lhag med
NK132(no)006:429: du zhi zhing / srid zhi'i dge legs kyi phun
NK132(no)006:430: sum tshogs pa'i yon tan ji snyed pa mtha' dag
NK132(no)006:431: yid la bsam pa bzhin du 'byor bar gyur cig
NK132(no)006:432: du zhi zhing / ces pa'o // de ltar zab don rdo rje'i gsung dbyangs nyid //
NK132(no)006:433: mos pa'i dbang gis cung zad bkral ba las //
NK132(no)006:434: ma rtogs log par rtog pa'i cha mchis na //
NK132(no)006:435: rtsa gsum srung ma'i spyan sngar mthol zhing bshags //
NK132(no)006:436: bdag rgyud rnam dpyod myu gu 'phel ba'i phyir //
NK132(no)006:437: 'jam mgon dgyes pa'i zhal gyi bum bzang las //
NK132(no)006:438: bskul gsung bdud rtsi'i thig phran 'thor ba'i tshe //
NK132(no)006:439: tshul 'di smra ba'i spobs pa cung zad rnyed //
NK132(no)006:440: de tshe rigs lam bye ba'i chu gter las //
NK132(no)006:441: rnam dpyod mgrin pa'i lam du yongs 'khyil ba //
NK132(no)006:442: mang thos drang srong dgyes pa'i zhal gyi lung //
NK132(no)006:443: dri med bdud rtsi'i klung dang 'grogs pa las //
NK132(no)006:444: bla ma'i drin gyis legs bshad cha yod na //
NK132(no)006:445: dge ba des ni mtha' yas 'gro ba kun //
NK132(no)006:446: rmad byung theg pa mchog la rab zhugs nas //
NK132(no)006:447: phyams gcig gdod ma'i gzhi la grol gyur cig /
NK132(no)006:448: ces pa 'di ni rigs thams cad kyi khyab bdag
NK132(no)006:449: bka' drin gzhal du med pa 'jam ma gon bla
NK132(no)006:450: ma kun mkhyen rdo rje gzi brjid kyis gsung gi
NK132(no)006:451: gnang ba stsal ba la brten /
NK132(no)006:452: mkhan chen pad+ma badz+ra las bshad lung mnos nas smon
NK132(no)006:453: lam rdo rje'i tshig gi rgya mdud kyi 'bru 'grel
NK132(no)006:454: cung zad 'god pa po ni mi pham blo gros
NK132(no)006:455: dri med ces bya ba rmongs brtul gyi na ba
NK132(no)006:456: bdag gis rdzong gsar bkra shis lha rtser bris pa
NK132(no)006:457: yin la / bla ma'i drin gyis bris par gyur
NK132(no)006:458: mod kyi ma rtogs pa dang log rtog gi cha
NK132(no)006:459: ni rang blo'i dri ma'i skyon yin pas mkhas pa'i
NK132(no)006:460: dbang po rnams la bshags shing /
NK132(no)006:461: dge bas bstan 'gro'i bde skyid thams cad yar ngo'i
NK132(no)006:462: dus kyi zla ba ltar gong nas gong du 'phel
